data.description: Spring is in the Air!!!  Check out this SW Minot Town-home with over 2000 sqft of living space! Located near the brand new trinity hospital, YMCA, the Dakota Square mall and many restaurants. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath has an open concept main floor, hard wood floors, large 6' privacy fenced yard with patio, modern kitchen with island and solid maple wood cabinets, heated garage, electric fireplaces, large master suite with huge walk-in closet and shower/jetted-tub combo bath with dual vanity. Beautiful property, definitely one you want to see, and in a prime and convenient location. Call your FAVORITE Realtor to see in person.
